#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kubrick; is a game based on the <trademark>Rubik's Cube</trademark> puzzle. "
"The cube sizes range from 2x2x2 up to 6x6x6, or you can play with irregular "
"<quote>bricks</quote> such as 5x3x2 or <quote>mats</quote> such as 6x4x1 or "
"2x2x1. The game has a selection of puzzles at several levels of difficulty, "
"as well as demos of pretty patterns and solution moves, or you can make up "
"your own puzzles ..."
msgstr ""
"&kubrick; je igrica bazirana na <trademark>Rubikova kocka </trademark> "
"slagalici.  Veličine kocke se kreću od  2x2x2  do 6x6x6, ili možete igrati "
"sa   nepravilnim <quote>ciglama</quote> kao što su 5x3x2 ili "
"<quote>strunjačama</quote> kao što su 6x4x1 ili 2x2x1. Igrica ima izbor "
"slagalica na nekoliko nivoa težine, kao i demose uzoraka i rješenja nekih "
"pokreta, ili možete napraviti sopstvene slagalice..."

