#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Često postavljana pitanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I pause the game?"
msgstr "Kako da zaustavim igricu?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kubrick; does not have a <quote>Pause</quote> feature, because none is "
"required. If a demo is running, just click anywhere to stop it."
msgstr ""
"&kubrick; nema <quote>Pauza</quote>svojsto , jer niko ne zahtjeva. Ako je "
"demo pokrenut, samo kliknite bilo gdje da ga zaustavite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change the way this game looks?"
msgstr "Mogu li promijeniti izgled igrice?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently you can change the view, using the <guimenu>View </guimenu> menu, "
"the amount and speed of animation and the bevel on the edges of the cubies, "
"using the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno možete promijeniti način prikaza, koristeći <guimenu>Prikaz </"
"guimenu> izbornik,  vrijednost i brzinu animacije i nagib na krajevima "
"kockica, koristeći <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> izbornik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Napravio/la sam grešku. Mogu li poništiti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. This is one of the strengths of &kubrick; as compared to a real puzzle. "
"You can undo and redo moves to any level, or undo all moves and start again. "
"To undo and redo moves, use the <guimenu>Move</guimenu> menu or the "
"corresponding keyboard shortcuts and toolbar buttons."
msgstr ""
"Da. Ovo je jedna od prednosti  &kubrick; u poređenju sa pravom slagalicom. "
"Možete poništiti i vratiti poteze na bilo koji level, ili poništiti sve "
"poteze i početi ponovo ispočetka. Da bi poništili i vrataili poteze, "
"koristite <guimenu>Potez</guimenu> izbornik ili korespondirajuće skraćenice "
"na tastaturi i dugmad trake alata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Mogu li koristiti tastaturu da igram ovu igricu?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes. &kubrick; has keyboard moves based on the X, Y and Z axes and others "
#| "based on Singmaster notation, which uses one-letter abbreviations for "
#| "Front, Back, Left, Right, Up and Down faces of the cube."
msgid ""
"Yes. &kubrick; has keyboard moves based on the X, Y and Z axes and others "
"based on <link linkend=\"singmaster-moves\">Singmaster notation</link>, "
"which uses one-letter abbreviations for Front, Back, Left, Right, Up and "
"Down faces of the cube."
msgstr ""
"Da.  &kubrick; ima poteze tastature bazirane na X,Y i Z osi i druge bazirane "
"na Singmaster bilješci, koji koristi jednoslovne skraćenice ( na engleskom "
"jeziku) za naprijed, nazad, lijevo, desno, gore i dolje (odnosi se na strane "
"kocke)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne mogu da otrkijem šta da radim? Imaju li neki savjeti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "No. However, the 3x3x3 <trademark>Rubik's Cube</trademark> has been "
#| "extensively analysed and you can find solution methods on the Internet "
#| "and in menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Demos</guimenu><guisubmenu>Solution "
#| "Moves</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> (<quote>Info</quote> item and "
#| "demonstrations of moves)."
msgid ""
"No. However, the 3x3x3 <trademark>Rubik's Cube</trademark> has been "
"extensively analysed and you can find solution methods on the Internet and "
"in menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Demos</guimenu><guisubmenu>Solution Moves</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> (the <guimenuitem>Info</guimenuitem> item and "
"demonstrations of moves)."
msgstr ""
"Ne. Kako god, 3x3x3 <trademark>Rubikova kocka</trademark>je bila opširno "
"analiziranaand i možete pronaći  metode rješavanja na Internetu ili u "
"stavkama menija<menuchoice><guimenu>Demos</guimenu><guisubmenu> Potezi "
"rješavanja</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> (<quote>Info</quote> stavke i "
"demonstracije rješavanja)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have to quit the game now. Can I save my position?"
msgstr "Moram da izađem iz igrice sada? Mogu li snimiti svoju poziciju?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:777
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes. In fact your position is saved automatically when you quit, just as "
#| "when you put a real cube back on the shelf. You can also save a "
#| "particular position by using menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Puzzle...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and the "
#| "corresponding shortcut keys and toolbar button."
msgid ""
"Yes. In fact your position is saved automatically when you quit, just as "
"when you put a real cube back on the shelf. You can also save a particular "
"position by using menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Save Puzzle…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and the corresponding "
"shortcut keys and toolbar button."
msgstr ""
"Da. U suptini Vaša pozicija se snima automatski kada vi izađete iz igrice, "
"baš kao kada odložite pravu kocku na policu. Možete također sačuvati "
"određenu poziciju koristeći stavke izbornika <menuchoice><guimenu>Igrica</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Snimi slagalicu...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> i "
"odgvarajuće prečac tipke i dugmad trake alata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I restore the game I saved?"
msgstr "Kako da vratim igricu koja je snimljena?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Your automatically saved game is restored automatically when you start "
#| "&kubrick;. To load other saved games, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Game </"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Load Saved Puzzle...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and "
#| "the corresponding shortcut keys and toolbar button."
msgid ""
"Your automatically saved game is restored automatically when you start "
"&kubrick;. To load other saved games, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Game </"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Load Puzzle…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and the "
"corresponding shortcut keys and toolbar button."
msgstr ""
"Vaša automatski snimljena igra je automatski vraćena kada pokrenete "
"&kubrick;. Da bi učitali neku drugu snimljenu igru,  koristite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igrica</guimenu><guimenuitem>Učitaj snimljenu igricu..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> i korespondirajuće prečac tipke i dugmad trake "
"alata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where are the high scores?"
msgstr "Gdje su najveće ocjene?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kubrick; does not have such a feature."
msgstr "&kubrick; nema takve značajke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igrice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To open a configuration (settings) dialog use one of the menubar items: "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kubrick; Game "
#| "Settings...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu> <guisubmenu>Choose Puzzle Type</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, sub-"
#| "menu <guimenuitem>Make Your Own...</guimenuitem> Only the latter dialog "
#| "has the options to change the cube dimensions and shuffling difficulty. "
#| "Below is a list of the options available."
msgid ""
"To open a configuration (settings) dialog use one of the menubar items: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kubrick; Game Settings…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Choose Puzzle Type</guisubmenu></menuchoice> with the "
"<guimenuitem>Make Your Own…</guimenuitem> option at the end, which will "
"display a dialog with options to change cube dimensions and shuffling "
"difficulty. Below is a list of the options available."
msgstr ""
"Da bi otvorili konfiguracioni (postavke) dijalog, koristite jednu od stavki "
"trake izbornika: <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Postavke igrice &kubrick; ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ili <menuchoice><guimenu>Igrica</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izaberi "
"tip slagalice</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, podizbornik <guimenuitem>Napravi "
"sopstvenu...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid "Watch shuffling in progress?"
msgstr "Gledanje miješanja u tijeku?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Provides an animated view of the cube when it is being shuffled by "
"the &kubrick; program.</action> You can select the speed of animation."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogućava animirani prikaz kocke dok se miješa od strane &kubrick; "
"programa.</action> Možete odabrati brzinu animacije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid "Watch your moves in progress?"
msgstr "Gledajte svoje poteze u tijeku?"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid "Provides an animated view of your own moves at a speed you can select."
msgstr "Osigurava animirani prikaz Vaših poteza u brzini koju odaberete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed of moves:"
msgstr "Brzina poteza:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:825
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Sets the speed at which animations go. </action> The range is 1 to "
"15 degrees of turn per animation frame."
msgstr ""
"<action>Postavlja brzinu animacije. </action>. Raspon brzine je od 1 do 15 "
"stepeni okreta po jednoma animacijskom okviru."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid "% of bevel on edges of cubies:"
msgstr "% kosine na rubovima kockica:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Sets the percentage of bevelled edge on each cubie, relative to the "
"size of the colored stickers.</action> It affects the overall shape of each "
"cubie. The range is from 4% to 30%."
msgstr ""
"<action>namješta procenat kosine na rubu svake kockice u odnosu na veličinu "
"svake obojene naljepnice</action> To utiče na ukupni oblik svake kockice. "
"Raspon je od 4% do 30%."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cube dimensions:"
msgstr "Dimenzije kocke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Sets the three dimensions of the cube, brick or mat in cubies per "
"side.</action> Dimensions can range from 2x2x1 up to 6x6x6: the larger the "
"dimensions, the harder the puzzle. Only one of the dimensions can be 1, "
"otherwise the puzzle becomes too easy."
msgstr ""
"<action>Podešava tri dimenzije kocke,,cigle, strunjače u kockicama po strani."
"</action> Raspon dimenzija može biti od 2x2x1 do 6x6x6: što su dimenzije "
"veće to je slagalica teža. Jedino jedna dimenzija može biti 1, u suprotnom "
"slagalica postaje previše lagana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves per shuffle (difficulty):"
msgstr "Potezi po miješanju (težina):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Sets the number of moves the &kubrick; program will use to shuffle "
"the cube.</action> The number can range from 0 to 50: the more moves, the "
"harder the puzzle. 2, 3 or 4 shuffling moves make for relatively easy "
"puzzles, especially if the shuffling moves can be watched."
msgstr ""
"<action>Postavlja broj poteza koji će &kubrick; program koristiti za "
"miješanje kocke.</action> Broj poteza je u rasponu od 0 do 50: što je veći "
"broj poteza to je slagalica teža. 2, 3 ili 4 poteza mješanja čine slagalicu "
"lakšom, pogotovo ako potezi mješanja se mogu gledati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting zero moves can be useful if you wish to experiment with different "
"sequences of moves and what they do to the cube, such as when you are "
"searching for pretty patterns or new solving moves."
msgstr ""
"Odabiranje nultog poteza može biti korisno ako želite eksperimentirati sa "
"različitim sekvencama poteza i šta one rade sa kockom, kao što tražite "
"odgovarajuće šablone ili nove poteze za rješavanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge i Licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kubrick; is Copyright 2008 Ian Wadham <email>ianw@netspace.net.au</email>"
msgstr ""
"&kubrick; je autorsko pravo 2008 Iana Wadhama <email>ianw@netspace.net.au</"
"email>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:871
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kubrick; was inspired by Professor Erno Rubik's famous "
#| "<trademark>Rubik's Cube </trademark> puzzle."
msgid ""
"&kubrick; was inspired by Professor Ern&odblac; Rubik's famous "
"<trademark>Rubik's Cube </trademark> puzzle."
msgstr ""
"&kubrick; je nadahnuta od strane  poznate <trademark>Rubikove Kocke</"
"trademark>slagalice profesora Erno Rubika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The programming is original work in C++ but owes several good ideas to the "
"Rubik XScreensaver, a C program by Marcelo Vianna, and GNUbik, a C program "
"by John M. Darrington."
